window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Two assassins. One deadly reckoning.</b></p> <p>John Milton thought he'd buried his past. But when Avi Bachman—an ex-Mossad killer and the most dangerous man Milton has ever known—escapes from a brutal Louisiana prison, vengeance brings them back on a collision course.</p> <p>As Bachman hunts the man he believes killed his wife, Milton seeks peace in the Australian outback. But violence finds him again, dragging him from the red dust of the outback to the streets of Tel Aviv, Hong Kong, and the back alleys of Eastern Europe.<br> <br> Bachmann is coming for him—only one of them will walk away.</p> <p><b><i>Headhunters</i></b> <b>is a relentless, globe-trotting thriller about revenge, redemption, and the ghosts that never stay buried.</b></p>"; 
